        }
        // Undefined variable: nm is read as a value but has no slot in this function
        // (not a param, global, or already-declared local — e.g. a typo or a local
        // that belongs to a different function). Mark it for a clean located error
        // instead of clang's internal "undefined value %nm_slot" (TVC-5002).
